<main class="garden-page">
  <header class="garden-page__header">
    <h1>Data Retention</h1>
    <p>Storage pressure from raw moisture readings on the Raspberry Pi. Completed calendar years can be summarized.</p>
  </header>

  <section class="garden-page__grid">
    <article class="garden-page__panel">
      <h2>Total Raw Readings</h2>
      <p><%= @moisture_readings_count %></p>
    </article>

    <article class="garden-page__panel">
      <h2>Before This Year</h2>
      <p><%= @previous_year_moisture_readings_count %></p>
    </article>

    <article class="garden-page__panel">
      <h2>Daily Summaries</h2>
      <p><%= @moisture_summary_count %></p>
    </article>

    <article class="garden-page__panel">
      <h2>Summary Crop Links</h2>
      <p><%= @moisture_summary_crop_count %></p>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="garden-page__panel">
    <h2>Summarize Completed Years</h2>
    <p>Process a few days before January 1 of the current year so the Raspberry Pi stays responsive.</p>
    <%= button_to "Summarize 3 Days",
                  maintenance_summarize_moisture_readings_path(max_days: 3),
                  method: :post,
                  data: {
                    confirm: "Summarize and delete raw moisture readings before January 1 of this year for up to 3 days?",
                    turbo_confirm: "Summarize and delete raw moisture readings before January 1 of this year for up to 3 days?"
                  } %>
  </section>
</main>
